    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "When installing moving parts such as bearings and pistons, always apply new, unused engine oil on the contact surfaces.\nPlace disassembled parts such as bearings and bearing caps in correct order and direction.\nWhen tightening connecting rod bolts and main bearing cap bolts, apply engine oil to threads and seating surface of nuts.",
